For Tomcat 9 we need atleast java 8 and above and for Tomcat Jre is enough but for maven we need Jdk which includes both Jre and additional tools as well.

Root
            |
         -------
        |       |
       JRE     JDK


       JRE
        |
   ------------
  |            |
Libraries     JVM


        JDK
         |
   ----------------
  |                |
JRE            Tools
